Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:31.76,Narration,Priestess Narrator,0,0,0,,At first, I just wanted to become \Nan adventurer so I could help people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:43.35,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,At least... that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:49.37,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I want to be an adventurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:55.95,Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1503,1)\c&HB3B9B6&\an2\pos(960,808.6)}Special Episode: The Priestess's Log
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.20,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,You're a priestess, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.70,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:06.39,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I'm an adult now, so I wanted \Nto help other adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:10.13,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,This will act as your ID in the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:17.49,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,Your identification tag shows that your rank \Nis porcelain, the lowest rank for adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:19.55,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,So I'm a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:20.62,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:26.21,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,It will also help identify you if something were to happen to you, so make sure not to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:26.90,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:29.83,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,And that ends your registration.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.83,0:01:32.48,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,You can find quests on the board there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:35.21,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,Please go ahead and find one suitable for your rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:38.39,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,Or you could join a veteran adventurer's party and—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:41.18,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna go adventuring with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:41.95,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.66,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,You're a priestess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:51.41,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,My party's missing a priest and we've got an urgent quest. So we were looking for at least one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:52.75,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Would you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.47,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,An urgent quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.31,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,We're gonna go slay some goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.18,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:07.82,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Yeah, they attacked a village, stole supplies \Nand livestock, and even kidnapped some girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:09.76,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,We need to hurry up and save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:13.49,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,Um... You're all porcelain-ranked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.90,Main,Guild girl,0,0,0,,I'm sure if you wait a little while, \Nother adventurers will show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.64,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,With the four of us, we shouldn't have \Nany trouble dealing with goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.16,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:25.05,Main,Fighter,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:26.41,Main,Wizard,0,0,0,,Make up your mind already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:34.30,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Okay. If you think that I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.59,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,On my first official quest,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.51,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to save a single person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.32,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:56.28,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.58,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.70,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.75,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.59,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.01,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:02.93,Main,Goblin Slayer,0,0,0,,That's one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.55,Main,Goblin Slayer,0,0,0,,And that makes two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.22,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Um... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.02,Main,Goblin Slayer,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:46.08,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,Within that dark cave, I met Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:53.22,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,He was not the kind of valiant hero \Nor savior that most would imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:05:00.44,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,All he cared about was killing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.92,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,slaying, and annihilating all the goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.03,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Children?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.03,Main,Goblin Slayer,0,0,0,,They multiply fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.77,Main,Goblin Slayer,0,0,0,,If we had waited any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:15.07,Main,Goblin Slayer,0,0,0,,there'd be about fifty of them, \Nand they would've attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.79,Main,Goblin Slayer,0,0,0,,You were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.34,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.23,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:26.78,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,They hold on to grudges for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:30.70,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,And the survivors of the nest learn \Nfrom their mistakes and adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.66,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,There isn't a single reason to let them live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.90,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Even if there was a good goblin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:44.79,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,A good goblin? I guess there might \Nbe one if you looked really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:49.28,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,But in the end, the only good goblins are \Nthe ones who never come out of their holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.95,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,That makes twenty-two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:42.03,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I had heard rumors that he had an unfortunate past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:50.09,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I'm not aware of the details of what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.03,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,but if that event hadn't occurred,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:58.13,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,he probably would've never taken the \Nmantle of Goblin Slayer upon himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:08.68,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,In order to find something I could do,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:13.46,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I decided to help Goblin Slayer slay goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:26.55,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,Eventually, we joined a group of adventurers who \Nwanted assistance in slaying hordes of the Demon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:30.00,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,O merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:34.72,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,please protect us, the weak, with the powers of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.86,Main,Ogre,0,0,0,,Iacta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.57,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.93,Main,Ogre,0,0,0,,What... What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.85,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,This is a gate scroll, linked to the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:27.19,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Now, then... What were you called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.03,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,I guess it doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.62,Main,Ogre,0,0,0,,Goblins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:33.93,Main,Ogre,0,0,0,,You would use this to kill mere goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:35.95,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Goblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.91,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,are far more troublesome than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:50.78,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,Right when we all got used to being in a party together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:55.64,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,we ended up facing the biggest threat of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.52,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:03.35,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,I can't tell how many but there's \Nsomething strange among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.60,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.37,Main,GS,0,0,0,,A hob... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:21.08,Main,GS,0,0,0,,A goblin champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.68,Main,GS,0,0,0,,We'll cut our way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.04,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Indeed. Let my blade assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.18,Main,P,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.27,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.55,Main,GS,0,0,0,,You can go all-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.57,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:07.54,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Damn it, there's a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.41,Main,DS,0,0,0,,No use complaining about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.03,Main,DS,0,0,0,,You holdin' up over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.34,Main,P,0,0,0,,Some... what...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.00,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.40,Main,P,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.32,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Orcbolg! Did they get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.97,Main,P,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.38,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,The Protection...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.57,Main,LP,0,0,0,,How could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.22,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Calm down and concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.14,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Long-ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:13.98,Main,DS,0,0,0,,You stupid goblins! Unhand her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.95,Main,P,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.01,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.70,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.74,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:18.06,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I heard that assassins like using string \Nmade of human hair as a killing tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.86,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Apparently it doesn't break easily or come undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:38.74,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Go! Hurry up and heal her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.30,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Thank you for the assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.95,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Orcbolg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.04,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Beard-cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.87,Main,LP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sir Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:47.13,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:53.83,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Hey, take a good look, goblin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:06.86,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.07,Main,GS,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.04,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Or you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:40.06,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Bless the stars. We somehow made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.88,Main,GS,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.07,Main,LP,0,0,0,,She will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:48.82,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Had the wound been any deeper, \Nthere would've been nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.53,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:57.04,Main,P,0,0,0,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.38,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:09.11,Main,P,0,0,0,,Gob... lin... Slay... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.90,Main,GS,0,0,0,,These things happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.14,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,U-Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.27,Main,P,0,0,0,,D-D-Did you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.11,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.50,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.07,Main,GS,0,0,0,,You don't have any scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:19.00,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I couldn't protect Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:24.71,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I was reminded of just how inexperienced I still was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.17,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,When I was young...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.42,Main,P,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:34.64,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I thought if I took a step, the ground \Nbeneath me would open up and I would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:40.27,Main,gS,0,0,0,,There was a time when I hesitated \Nto even walk because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:45.90,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,It's not impossible, but no one worries about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.07,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,That was really strange to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.40,Main,GS,0,0,0,,She and my sister laughed at me for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:56.41,Main,GS,0,0,0,,but it took me a while to realize that I still have to walk, no matter how scared I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.61,Main,P,0,0,0,,So that how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.54,Main,GS,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:07.21,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,Even now, I'm scared to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.57,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,I'm thankful that you're helping me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:14.49,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,but you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:25.94,Main,P,0,0,0,,I told you I was going to do what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:27.88,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.76,Main,P,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:35.20,Main,P,0,0,0,,You really are hopeless, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.29,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:42.02,Main,P,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.75,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:51.94,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,And then, I realized that he was still \Nhaunted and tormented by the trauma of his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:56.87,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,When one of the most important \Npeople in his life was in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.47,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,He went...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:02.01,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,to slay some goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:36.73,Main,P,0,0,0,,O merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:41.53,Main,P,0,0,0,,please protect us, the weak, with the powers of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.87,Main,P,0,0,0,,Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:18.96,Main,GL,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:23.36,Main,GL,0,0,0,,I'll... never do anything like this again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.12,Main,GL,0,0,0,,I-I'll go back to the forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.12,Main,GL,0,0,0,,and live peacefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.29,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Like hell that's going to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:42.38,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Lord? Lord, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.97,Main,GS,0,0,0,,You're just a goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:49.08,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Just a filthy little goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.10,Main,GS,0,0,0,,And I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:58.59,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.64,Main,GS,0,0,0,,That's one goblin head...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:05.20,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:16.67,Main,P,0,0,0,,O merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:20.00,Main,P,0,0,0,,please place your gentle hand upon this being's wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.97,Main,P,0,0,0,,Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.21,Main,P,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:31.06,Main,P,0,0,0,,I ended up only using two Protections.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.73,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.81,Main,P,0,0,0,,Please don't push yourself so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.69,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I can't win if I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:40.82,Main,P,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:45.36,Main,P,0,0,0,,You said you wouldn't push yourself anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:50.91,Main,P,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:57.65,Main,P,0,0,0,,Please try to think things through a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:58.92,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:02.71,Main,GS,0,0,0,,It's because... I trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:10.54,Main,P,0,0,0,,You truly are such a hopeless person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:17.95,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer is truly hard to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:23.57,Narration,Priestess Narrator,0,0,0,,He barely speaks, and he doesn't care how he kills goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.04,Narration,Priestess Narrator,0,0,0,,He had fought alone for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:35.01,Narration,Priestess Narrator,0,0,0,,I want to help Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:43.76,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,To our fallen comrades, our victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:47.82,Main,Hea,0,0,0,,the farm, the town, adventurers and of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:52.04,Main,Hea,0,0,0,,that weirdo over there who never \Ntalks about anything but goblins!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:53.43,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:56.72,Main,All,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:13.35,Main,P,0,0,0,,Hey, Goblin Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:17.43,Main,P,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I ask for a reward, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:18.50,Main,GS,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:24.78,Main,P,0,0,0,,Please take off your helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:27.42,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:32.64,Main,P,0,0,0,,I kept my eyes closed that other time \Nbecause I was so embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.85,0:23:56.16,Main,P,0,0,0,,I think you look a lot cooler this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:59.87,Main,LP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah, now this is the face of a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:03.79,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I am no longer the newbie adventurer with silly dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:00.90,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey... Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:04.94,Main,DS,0,0,0,,{\an8}You have excellent features indeed, Beard-cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:07.67,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I hope that I can now provide a ray of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:07.67,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:13.92,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,to those cowering in despair, deep within a dark cave, crying and calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:23.90,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,Right now, my hope is that I can be \Nlike the person that I admire so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:32.82,Main,P,0,0,0,,If you ever need help, we'll always be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:36.72,Main,P,0,0,0,,So, it has nothing to do with luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.72,0:24:37.58,Main,P,0,0,0,,at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.77,0:24:40.98,Main,Gs,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:44.17,Main,GS,0,0,0,,That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.21,0:24:53.57,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,I'm still going on many adventures with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.72,0:25:04.78,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,The other day, we received a letter asking Goblin Slayer if he would save some adventurers who were in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.83,0:25:07.17,Narration,P Narrator,0,0,0,,And then...
